					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p62008">OAM reading isn't reliable</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=62008&amp;sid=f0a1ad086f3425b68b191f4ca4a80224#p62008"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Fri May 28, 2010 6:35 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
