					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I'm getting a feeling that OAM was never meant to be read, that the read functionality was meant exactly for what Micro Machines does. That would explain why reading doesn't increment the address (so it wouldn't disturb when you read while PPU rendering is occurring). Still probing this behavior, right now writing a program to see whether OAM even works as expected on the one PPU-CPU alignment that seems normal.</div>

